Description
This server does not contain any special NPCs like Buff NPCs.
We want to give our players the feeling of old official servers. That's why we won't destroy the gameplay by providing overpowered donation items.
Features

    2013 Client with Pre-Renewal Mechanics
    No 3rd Classes
    Mounts
    Costumes
    No KVM Weapons
    No Overpowered Items
    Custom Dungeon Warper Quest System
    Unique Item Collect Quest System
    Unique Battleground Equipment
    InternalGuard Protection
        WPE/RPE
        Bots
        Macros
        Client Modifications
        other 3rd Party Tools
    Custom Login Protection
    Fair Cash Shop
    Zeny to Cash Shop Credits Trader (you can use the cash shop without spending real life money!)
    Navigation System
    Homunculus System
    Cart Extensions
    WoE
    PvP
    Support System (not done yet)
